A man is due to appear before the Giyani Magistrate Court on Monday on a charge of murder.The 22-year-old man was arrested on Saturday for the brutal murder of a 17-year-old girl who is a Grade 11 learner at Mukula High School in Nsavulani village outside Giyani.According to police the man allegedly broke into the teenager&#8217;s home, where she was sleeping alone and stabbed her multiple times.The motive of this killing is still unknown and police investigations are still continuing.-TNA Reporter 